title: Silver 2 jungle main looking for duo
body:
Just finished my braindead ranking games won 6 lost 4 and ended up in silver. I play solo all the time but having a reliable partner who doesn't feed often or flame would be a blessing. I don't play often so other roles such as bot, mid, top I have little to no interest in as I haven't exactly played them enough. 

Invite me if you want to go mess around and play a few games xd  {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

replies.body: Hey, i would be glad to duo with you, find me at https://discord.gg/Y93kJJN
